Syslog Configuration:
=====================

  R1(config)# logging on // enables logging of Syslog messages

  Option 01 => R1(config)# logging 192.168.10.100 // destination where the messages are saved

  Option 02 => R1(config)# logging host 192.168.10.100

  R1(config)# logging trap debugging 

Verification:
=============

  # show logging
